      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on its established performance in rotating machinery and transitional flow regimes. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model is the standard regulatory-accepted formulation. Qualitative justification documented; formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at Gradation 1."
    },
