      "rationale": "All model inputs (geometry dimensions, fluid viscosity, hematocrit, rotational speed, flow rates) are documented with sources in the simulation plan. Nominal values drawn from FDA pump specifications and experimental setup records. Input sensitivity analysis is not required at Gradation 1."
