    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 and documented at that level. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions are within acceptable agreement with experimental data across all five operating points. The package is accepted for regulatory submission support.",
